       <em>We intend to promote Portuguese participation through the publication and use of data</em>
       <p><a href="https://www.gbif.pt" target="_blank"><img src="<?php print $base_path?>sites/all/themes/gbifBootstrap-1.0/gbifBootstrap/images/GBIFPORTUGAL-01.png" class="img-rounded img-responsive center-block" alt="Nó Português do GBIF" title="Nó Português do GBIF"/></a></p>
       <h2>Vision</h2>
       <p>Free and open sharing of primary biodiversity data enriches knowledge and value of Portuguese and global biodiversity.</p>
       <h2>Mission</h2>
       <p>To promote the integration of Portuguese data providers and biodiversity information resources into the GBIF network, and the availability of biodiversity data for scientific research and to be used by society.
